T1	Intervention 450 851	Patients with large, potentially operable, locally-advanced breast cancer were randomized to receive anastrozole (1 mg/day) plus tamoxifen placebo or tamoxifen (20 mg/day) plus anastrozole placebo pre-operatively. After surgery at 3 months, patients continued on the same study medication as adjuvant therapy for up to 5 years or until recurrence, intolerable toxicity or withdrawal of patient consent
